2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with a MIMO two way cellular network, which is a networking topic. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes algorithms for joint precoding design, which can be considered as a control problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with transmission of signals in a cellular network, which can be considered as a multimedia application. 
5. cs.COM (Computers and Society) - This is the least likely category, but the paper may have some implications for the societal impact of cellular networks.
